Class ButtonContext

  • java.lang.Object
    • cs505.group1.state.ButtonContext
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ButtonAContext

    public abstract class ButtonContext
extends java.lang.Object
    An abstract framework for developing and using contexts in a finite state machine to set actions generated by a GrovePi button sensor.
